quran[58]{c,v,t}:
  37,145,"ftrhnah min batan alhwt, walqynah fi 'ard khaliat eariat min alshajar walbna', wahu daeif albdn"
  37,146,"wanbtna ealayh shajaratan min alqare tzlluh, wyntfe bha"
  37,147,"warslnah 'iilaa miayat 'alf min qawmih bal yzydwn, fsddaqu waeamiluu bima ja' bh, famataenahum bhyathm 'iilaa waqt bulugh ajalhm"
  37,148,"warslnah 'iilaa miayat 'alf min qawmih bal yzydwn, fsddaqu waeamiluu bima ja' bh, famataenahum bhyathm 'iilaa waqt bulugh ajalhm"
  37,149,"fasal -ayha alrswl- qwmk: kayf jaealuu lilah albanat allaati ykrhwnhnna, wlanfshm albanin aladhin yrydwnhm?"
  37,150,"wasalhm akhalaqna almalayikat 'inathana, wahum hadrwn?"
  37,151,"w'inn min kdhbhm qwlhm: wlad allh, wa'iinahum lkadhbwn; li'anahum yaqulun ma la yelmwn"
  37,152,"w'inn min kdhbhm qwlhm: wlad allh, wa'iinahum lkadhbwn; li'anahum yaqulun ma la yelmwn"
  37,153,lay shay' yakhtar allah albanat dun albnyn?
  37,154,"bys alhukm ma thkmwnh -ayha alqwm- 'an yakun lilah albanat walakum albnwn, wa'antum la tardawn albanat lanfskm"
  37,155,afla tadhakarun 'anah la yajuz wala ynbghy 'an yakun lah wld? taealaa allah ean dhlk elwwana kbyrana
  37,156,bl 'alakum hujat byint ealaa qawlukum waftraykm?
  37,157,"'in kanat lakum hujat fi kitab min eind allah fatuu bha, 'iin kuntum sadiqin fi qwlkm?"
  37,158,"wjel almushrikun bayn allah walmalayikat qurabat wnsbana, walaqad ealimat almalayikat 'ana almushrikin muhdarun lledhab yawm alqyamt"
  37,159,tnzzah allah ean kl ma la ylyq bih mmma ysfh bih alkafrwn
  37,160,lkn eibad allah almukhlasin lah fi eibadatih la ysfwnh 'iilaa bima ylyq bjlalh sbhanh
  37,161,"f'inkm -ayha almushrikun ballh- wama taebudun min dun allah min alht, ma 'antum bmdllin ahdana 'iilaa man qddar allah eaza wajala ealayh 'an yaslaa aljhym; lkfrh wzlmh"
  37,162,"f'inkm -ayha almushrikun ballh- wama taebudun min dun allah min alht, ma 'antum bmdllin ahdana 'iilaa man qddar allah eaza wajala ealayh 'an yaslaa aljhym; lkfrh wzlmh"
  37,163,"f'inkm -ayha almushrikun ballh- wama taebudun min dun allah min alht, ma 'antum bmdllin ahdana 'iilaa man qddar allah eaza wajala ealayh 'an yaslaa aljhym; lkfrh wzlmh"
  37,164,"qalt almlaykt: wama minaa ahd 'iilaa lah maqam fi alsama' melwm, wa'iinaa lanahn alwaqfwn sfwfana fi eibadat allah wtaeth, wa'iinaa lanahn almnzzihwn allah ean kl ma la ylyq bh"
  37,165,"qalt almlaykt: wama minaa ahd 'iilaa lah maqam fi alsama' melwm, wa'iinaa lanahn alwaqfwn sfwfana fi eibadat allah wtaeth, wa'iinaa lanahn almnzzihwn allah ean kl ma la ylyq bh"
  37,166,"qalat almlaykt: wama minaa ahd 'iilaa lah maqam fi alsama' melwm, wa'iinaa lanahn alwaqfwn sfwfana fi eibadat allah wtaeth, wa'iinaa lanahn almnzzihwn allah ean kl ma la ylyq bh"
  37,167,"w'in kafaar \"mk\" layaqulun qabl bethtk -ayha alrswl-: law ja'ana min alkutub walanbya' ma ja' al'awalin qblna, lakunaa eibad allah alsaadiqin fi al'iyman, almkhlasyn fi alebadt"
  37,168,"w'in kafaar \"mk\" layaqulun qabl bethtk -ayha alrswl-: law ja'ana min alkutub walanbya' ma ja' al'awalin qblna, lakunaa eibad allah alsaadiqin fi al'iyman, almkhlasyn fi alebadt"
  37,169,"w'in kafaar \"mk\" layaqulun qabl bethtk -ayha alrswl-: law ja'ana min alkutub walanbya' ma ja' al'awalin qblna, lakunaa eibad allah alsaadiqin fi al'iyman, almkhlasyn fi alebadt"
  37,170,"flma ja'ahum dhakar alawlyn, waealam alakharina, wa'akmal alktb, wa'afdal alrsl, wahu muhamad salaa allah ealayh wslm, kafaruu bh, fasawf yaelamun ma lahum min aleadhab fi alakhrt"
  37,171,"wlqd sabaqat kalimatuna -alty laa mrdd lha- lieibadina almrslyn, 'ana lahum alnsrt ealaa aedayhm balhjt walqwt, wa'ana jundana almujahidin fi sabilana lahum alghalibun laedayhm fi kl maqam biaietibar aleaqibat walmal"
  37,172,"wlqd sabaqat kalimatuna -alty laa mrdd lha- lieibadina almrslyn, 'ana lahum alnsrt ealaa aedayhm balhjt walqwt, wa'ana jundana almujahidin fi sabilana lahum alghalibun laedayhm fi kl maqam biaietibar aleaqibat walmal"
  37,173,"wlqd sabaqat kalimatuna -alty laa mrdd lha- lieibadina almrslyn, 'ana lahum alnsrt ealaa aedayhm balhjt walqwt, wa'ana jundana almujahidin fi sabilana lahum alghalibun laedayhm fi kl maqam biaietibar aleaqibat walmal"
  37,174,"faerd -ayha alrswl- eamman eand, walam yaqbal alhaqu hataa tnqdy almudat alty 'amhilhum fyha, wayati 'amr allah bedhabhm, wanzrhm wartqb madha yahilu bihim min aleadhab bmkhalftk? fasawf yarawn ma yahilu bihim min eadhab allh"
  37,175,"fa'aerid -ayha alrswl- eamman eand, walam yaqbal alhaqu hataa tnqdy almudat alty 'amhilhum fyha, wayati 'amr allah bedhabhm, wanzrhm wartqb madha yahilu bihim min aleadhab bmkhalftk? fasawf yarawn ma yahilu bihim min eadhab allh"
  37,176,"afbnzwl edhabna bihim yastaejilunak 'ayuha alrswl? fa'iidha nazal edhabna bhm, fabis alsabah sbahhm"
  37,177,"afbnzwl edhabna bihim yastaejilunak 'ayuha alrswl? fa'iidha nazal edhabna bhm, fabis alsabah sbahhm"
  37,178,"waerd eanhum hataa yadhan allah bedhabhm, wanzrhm fasawf yarawn ma yahilu bihim min aleadhab walnkal"
  37,179,"waerd eanhum hataa yadhan allah bedhabhm, wanzrhm fasawf yarawn ma yahilu bihim min aleadhab walnkal"
  37,180,tnzzah allah wteala rabi aleizat eamaa ysfh hwla' almftrwn elyh
  37,181,wthyt allah alddayimat wthnawh wamanh lajamie almrslyn
  37,182,"walhmd lilah rabi alealamin fi al'uwlaa walakhrt, fahu almsthq ldhlk wahdah la sharik lh"
  38,1,(s) sabaq alkalam ealaa alhrwf almqttaet fi 'awal surat albqrt
  38,2,(s) sabaq alkalam ealaa alhrwf almqttaet fi 'awal surat albqrt
  38,3,"kthyrana min al'umam 'ahlaknaha qabl hwla' almshrkyn, fastghathu hin ja'ahum aleadhab wanadawa baltwbt, walays alwaqt waqt qabwl twbt, wala waqt firar wkhlas mimaa asabhm"
  38,4,"wejib hwla' alkufaar min baeath allah 'iilayhim basharana mnhm; lydewhm 'iilaa allah wykhwwafhm edhabh, wqalu: 'iinah lays rasulana bal hu kadhib fi qwlh, sahir lqwmh, kayf ysyir alalihat alkathirat 'ilhana wahdana? 'inn hdha aladhi ja' bih wadaea 'iilayh lashy' ejyb"
  38,5,"wejib hwla' alkufaar min baeath allah 'iilayhim basharana mnhm; lydewhm 'iilaa allah wykhwwafhm edhabh, wqalu: 'iinah lays rasulana bal hu kadhib fi qwlh, sahir lqwmh, kayf ysyir alalihat alkathirat 'ilhana wahdana? 'inn hdha aladhi ja' bih wadaea 'iilayh lashy' ejyb"
  38,6,"wantalaq ruasa' alqawm wkbrawhm yhrridwn qawmahum ealaa alaistimrar ealaa alshirk walsbr ealaa taeadud alalht, wayaqulun 'iina ma ja' bih hdha alrasul shay' mdbbar yuqsad minh alriyasat walsyadt, ma samiena bima yadeu 'iilayh fi din abayina min qrysh, wala fi alnsranyt, ma hdha 'iilaa kadhab waftra'"
  38,7,"wantlq ruasa' alqawm wkbrawhm yhrridwn qawmahum ealaa alaistimrar ealaa alshirk walsbr ealaa taeadud alalht, wayaqulun 'iina ma ja' bih hdha alrasul shay' mdbbar yuqsad minh alriyasat walsyadt, ma samiena bima yadeu 'iilayh fi din abayina min qrysh, wala fi alnsranyt, ma hdha 'iilaa kadhab waftra'"
  38,8,"akhus muhamad bnzwl alquran ealayh min dwnna? bal hum fi rayb min whyy 'iilayk -ayha alrswl- w'irsaly lk, bal qaluu dhlk; li'anahum lm yadhuquu eadhab allh, falaw dhaquu eadhabah lamaa tjrwu ealaa ma qalu"
  38,9,"am hum yamlikun khazayin fadal rabik aleaziz fi sltanh, alwahhab ma yasha' min rizqih wfdlh liman yasha' min khlqh?"
  38,10,"am lhwla' almushrikin mulk alsmwat wal'ard wama bynhma, fyuetu wyamneu? flyakhdhu balasbab almwslt lahum 'iilaa alsma', hataa yhkmu bima yuridun min eata' wmne"
  38,11,"hwla' aljnd almkdhdhibwn jund mhzwmwn, kama huzm ghyrhm min al'ahzab qblhm, kdhdhabt qablahum qawm nuh waead wafireawn sahib alquat alezymt, wathamud waqawm lut wa'ashab al'ashjar walbsatyn wahum qawm sheyb. 'uwlayik al'umam aladhin thzzabu ealaa alkufr waltkdhyb wajtmeu elyh. 'in kll min hwla' 'iilaa kdhdhab alrsl, fasthqu eadhab allh, whll bihim eqabh"
  38,12,"hwla' aljnd almkdhdhibwn jund mhzwmwn, kama huzm ghyrhm min al'ahzab qblhm, kdhdhabt qablahum qawm nuh waead wafireawn sahib alquat alezymt, wathamud waqawm lut wa'ashab al'ashjar walbsatyn wahum qawm sheyb. 'uwlayik al'umam aladhin thzzabu ealaa alkufr waltkdhyb wajtmeu elyh. 'in kll min hwla' 'iilaa kdhdhab alrsl, fasthqu eadhab allh, whll bihim eqabh"
  38,13,"hwla' aljnd almkdhdhibwn jund mhzwmwn, kama huzm ghyrhm min al'ahzab qblhm, kdhdhabt qablahum qawm nuh waead wafireawn sahib alquat alezymt, wathamud waqawm lut wa'ashab al'ashjar walbsatyn wahum qawm sheyb. 'uwlayik al'umam aladhin thzzabu ealaa alkufr waltkdhyb wajtmeu elyh. 'in kll min hwla' 'iilaa kdhdhab alrsl, fasthqu eadhab allh, whll bihim eqabh"
  38,14,"hwla' aljnd almkdhdhibwn jund mhzwmwn, kama huzm ghyrhm min al'ahzab qblhm, kdhdhabt qablahum qawm nuh waead wafireawn sahib alquat alezymt, wathamud waqawm lut wa'ashab al'ashjar walbsatyn wahum qawm sheyb. 'uwlayik al'umam aladhin thzzabu ealaa alkufr waltkdhyb wajtmeu elyh. 'in kll min hwla' 'iilaa kdhdhab alrsl, fasthqu eadhab allh, whll bihim eqabh"
  38,15,"wma yantazir hwla' almushrikun lhlwl aleadhab ealayhim 'iina baquu ealaa shrkhm, 'iilaa nafkhat wahidat ma laha min rjwe"
  38,16,"wqalu: rabana ejjil lana nsybna min aleadhab fi aldyna qabl yawm alqyamt, wakan hdha asthza'an mnhm"
  38,17,"asbr -ayha alrswl- ealaa ma yqwlwnh mimaa tkrh, wadhkur eabdana dawud sahib alquat ealaa 'aeda' allah walsbr ealaa taeth, 'iinah twwab kthyr alrujue 'iilaa ma yurdi allh. (wfy hdha tslyt llrswl salaa allah ealayh wslm)"
  38,18,"'ina skhkharna aljibal mae dawud ysbbihn btsbyhh 'awal alnahar wakhrh, wasakharna altayr maeah majmueat tsbbih, wttye tbeana lh"
  38,19,"'iinaa skhkharna aljibal mae dawud ysbbihn btsbyhh 'awal alnahar wakhrh, wasakharna altayr maeah majmueat tsbbih, wttye tbeana lh"
  38,20,"wqwwayna lah mulkah balhybt walquat walnsr, wataynah alnbwt, walfsl fi alkalam walhkm"